full_text: Marinating on the 'camera going dark, reveal' ending to Dynamite, man...what a total whiff. It reeked of WWE having some gigantic dude no one knows be treated as someone we should a) know or b) be impressed by in 2022. Real mess.
At this point the Bruins can lose out, and all that really matters is getting everyone as close to 100% as possible. Team health in shambles.
